Original package:
https://www.npmjs.com/package/@tencent-weixin/openclaw-weixin

First-party modifications in this package include:
- Multi-account concurrent QR session management in src/weixin/auth/login-qr.ts
- Extended config schema with demoService support in src/weixin/config/config-schema.ts
- Local web management console in src/weixin/service/
- Plugin entry registration for clawbnb-hub

Maintenance note:
- The upstream-derived protocol/runtime layer is treated as constrained.
- Ongoing work should stay in the local service layer, packaging, and documentation unless a compatibility fix is required.
